name: Laws of Karma — #12 Law of Significance and Inspiration
description:
This is the last piece of "Laws of Karma" collection, my first collection ever on HEN. Time flies, huh? If you read this description, please know that I'm thankful for you. Thank you for keeping me inspired and motivated this whole time.

This piece is trying to say that whatever you do and give to the world; low effort, high effort, small value, big value; all will create impacts and differences to the future.

So, sail with your best effort, friends. See you on the next collection.
